Giant centipede venom causes severe muscle stiffness.
Saving Throw DC 17 Fortitude; Maximum Duration 6 rounds;
Stage 1 1d4 poison damage (1 round); Stage 2 1d4 poison damage and fatigued (1 round); Stage 3 1d4 poison damage, clumsy 1, and fatigued (1 round)

Saving Throw DC 18 Fortitude; Maximum Duration 4 hours;
Stage 1 slowed 1 (1 round); Stage 2 slowed 1 (1 minute);
Stage 3 unconscious with no Perception check to wake up (1 round); Stage 4 unconscious with no Perception check to wake up (1d4 hours)
